thumb that some people use is

00:31:26.230 --> 00:31:29.400
that if it's just
about teenagers,

00:31:29.400 --> 00:31:32.420
but it's for grown-ups there
will be a sense of looking back

00:31:32.420 --> 00:31:34.850
on what happened from
the grown-up perspective.

00:31:34.850 --> 00:31:36.210
